Sesuai untuk penuntut, pengkaji dan penggemar sejarah mencungkil falsafah dan tamadun Islam di bandar-bandar utama dunia yang pernah memayungi umat Islam satu ketika dulu. Seperti yang kerap kita temui di kehidupan nyata, pasangan suami isteri sering mendapat pertanyaan bila akan mendapat cahaya mata. Pertanyaan itulah yang sering kali disoal kepada Arga dan Salsa selepas bernikah.

Beliau mendidik kanak-kanak dan umat islam di wilayah ini dan istimewanya adalah beliau menggunakan Bahasa melayu dan jawi sebagai Bahasa penhantar dalam pendidikan beliau.

programme.title: Setia Menunggumu Ep5
programme.desc: Ramlan sering mengingatkan Adi supaya jangan ganggu Aida lagi kerana dia akan bertunang dengan Aida. Tetapi Adi telah bertanyakan sendiri kepada Aida, benarkah dia akan bertunang dengan Ramlan, Aida telah memberikan jawapan tidak. Adi terlihat Ramlan menjual dadah kepada budak-budak kampung, lalu dia melaporkan perkara ini kepada pihak polis. Ramlan telah menyerang Adi kerana Adi masih rapat lagi dengan Aida, tiba-tiba waktu itu datang sepasukan polis. Kenapakah polis datang kepada mereka? Apakah yang terjadi kepada mereka?

Selain itu, Ustaz ada menyenaraikan 3 jenis tanda orang yang munafik. Soalan seterusnya mengenai berniaga. programme.desc: Cansu dan Deniz terkejut apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa Ezgi pergi ke Gcek dengan zgr mengikut perjanjian. Walaupun Ozan menyedari dia telah menumpahkan rahsia itu pada saat-saat akhir, dia perlu menjelaskan segala-galanya dengan tekanan Deniz. Cansu dan Deniz tidak selesa. Oleh kerana mereka takut bahawa Ezgi akan jatuh cinta dengan zgr, mereka mengejar mereka dan pergi ke Gcek. Sementara itu, hari yang penuh dengan pengembaraan dan ketegangan menanti Ezgi dan zgr, yang jatuh di pulau terbiar akibat masalah yang mereka alami, dan rakan serta keluarga mereka yang tidak dapat menghubungi mereka sedang mencari mereka di merata tempat dengan panik.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep15
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam (Angah) dan Mizan (Along) dua beradik dari satu keluarga. Nizam lulusan luar negeri, bekerjaya, baru berkahwin dan baru juga bercerai. Hubungan Nizam dan Mizan tidak mesra sangat. ibu bapa mereka juga memelihara Hani, sebagai adik angkat. Kini, Hani seorang gadis, selain sangat disayangi ibu bapa mereka, Mizan pula mencintainya. Jalinan percintaan mereka juga direstui ibu bapa mereka, cuma Nizam terpaksa menangguhkan perkahwinan mereka sekurang-kurangnya 3 tahun kerana melanjutkan pelajaran keluar negara. Hani yang baik sahsiahnya dan berbudi pekerti, pandai mengemas rumah tangga memahaminya dan sanggup menunggu. Di hari ketibaan Nizam pulang, ibu bapanya telah menetapkan sebagai hari perkahwinan Nizam dan Hani. Selain majlis telah siap, tetamu juga telah dijemput, tiba-tiba sehari sebelum majlis berlangsung, Nizam meminta majlis dibatalkan dengan alasan dia telah berkahwin 5 bulan lalu. Di hari itu, Mizan juga pulang sebagai meraikan majlis adiknya, lalu ibu bapanya mencadangkan Mizan menggantikan tempat Nizam. Mizan agak terkejut dan tidak bersetuju walau pun dirayu demi menutup maruah keluarga. Sementara itu Hani amat berduka, tetapi sebelah malamnya Hani berubah hati semata-mata demi maruah keluarga lalu merayu beberapa kali kepada Mizan mengambilnya sebagai isteri. Mizan bukan sahaja menolak permintaan Hani, sebaliknya mencerca Hani yang dianggap tidak malu. Hani pula terus berdoa. Di awal pagi hari majlis, Mizan berubah hati dan bersetuju. Majlis perkahwinan Mizan dan Hani serta jamuan berjalan lancar. Di sebelah petangnya. Nizam dan isterinya, Shela juga tiba dan mereka dijangka akan tinggal di situ beberapa ketika.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep27
programme.desc: Selepas semua kekecewaan Ezgi menuju ke Bursa untuk membersihkan kepalanya. Nevin dan nal mempersoalkan keadaan Ezgi ini. Walaupun Ezgi menyembunyikan pengalamannya dengan zgr, semuanya terbongkar apabila zgr datang ke Bursa. Permohonan maaf zgr tidak mengubah apa-apa. zgr tidak mempercayainya, yang menyebabkan dia sangat kecewa. Semakin zgr menyendiri, semakin dia merindui Ezgi dan semakin dia menyedari betapa dia menyayanginya. Keadaan fikiran ini mengaktifkan Ozan. Cansu dan Deniz juga kecewa dan menyesal kerana mereka melayan Ezgi dengan salah. Mereka juga bekerjasama dengan Ozan dan cuba membawa Ezgi dan zgr bersama.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep28
programme.desc: Ezgi sangat terharu dengan kejutan zgr. Semua kebencian terhadap zgr berlalu. Dalam proses ini, kedua-duanya lebih memahami betapa mereka menghargai satu sama lain. Mereka membuka lembaran baru dalam hubungan mereka, tidak ada lagi tempat untuk pembohongan. Jadi mereka memutuskan untuk memberitahu keluarga mereka bahawa mereka bersama. Nevin menerima perhubungan ini walaupun dia tidak menginginkannya sangat, Sevim pula tidak mahu Ezgi dan zgr bersama. Ezgi mengadakan acara pertamanya di syarikat organisasi yang diupahnya, dan kejutan menantinya di acara ini. Sementara itu, Serdar mengambil tindakan sekali lagi untuk mendapatkan Ezgi, tetapi apabila dia mengetahui bahawa zgr dan Ezgi bersama, dia kecewa dan keadaan ini menjadikannya lebih bercita-cita tinggi.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep29
programme.desc: zgr menjadi marah apabila dia mengetahui bahawa Tolga ialah bos Ezgi. Ezgi segera berhenti. Tetapi Tolga tidak akan selesa sehingga dia mendapat La Gabbia, dia telah pun membuat perancangan untuk meletakkan Ezgi dalam situasi yang sukar dengan sokongan Gizem. Dia mengambil kesempatan daripada kelemahan zgr untuk Ezgi. Apabila bercakap mengenai Ezgi, ia menjadi lebih sukar bagi zgr untuk membuat keputusan menentang kehendak Tolga. Sementara itu, zgr berurusan dengan restoran baharu dan pembukaannya. Terhadap semua kesukaran, perkara yang paling penting bagi zgr dan Ezgi ialah cinta mereka antara satu sama lain. Tetapi Tolga dan Serdar tidak berniat untuk membiarkan mereka bersendirian.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep30
programme.desc: Ezgi dan zgr, yang melihat polis di hadapan mereka, terkejut. zgr, yang menganggap Tolga mengadu tentang Ezgi, menjadi gila. Mereka semua perlu pergi ke balai polis bersama-sama. Walaupun Ezgi, yang keterangannya diambil, dikeluarkan, mereka tidak melepaskan kerja ini dan cuba membuktikan Ezgi tidak bersalah. Terhadap semua kesukaran, perkara yang paling penting bagi zgr dan Ezgi ialah cinta mereka antara satu sama lain. Tetapi Tolga dan Serdar tidak berniat untuk membiarkan mereka bersendirian. Sementara itu, Ezgi telah menyediakan pesta bujang mengejut untuk Cansu. Cansu sangat gembira dapat berseronok dengan gadis-gadis itu. Emre juga tidak berdiam diri dan menyediakan kejutan untuk Levent. Tetapi kejutan ini tidak akan menggembirakan gadis-gadis itu.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep31
programme.desc: Selepas bertemu Serdar di Gcek, Ezgi dan zgr mula berfikir tentang apa yang perlu dilakukan apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa Serdar juga akan menghadiri majlis perkahwinan Ebru. Rakan-rakan mereka cuba mencari idea dan membantu mereka untuk meneruskan perkahwinan. Sementara itu, Sevim dan Nevin bergaul dengan baik, dan dengan bimbingan Fitnat, mereka mula merancang untuk mengatasi Ezgi dan zgr. Ezgi dan zgr juga berpura-pura tidak sesuai antara satu sama lain agar tidak menyusahkan keluarga mereka. Ini membuatkan keluarga mereka sangsi dengan perkahwinan mereka berdua.

Tok Guru Nik Ahmad mula melatih pelajar pondoknya main bola. Tapi Cikgu Roslan kemudian cadangkan agar dibuat pencarian siapa pelajar pondok yang sehat dan kuat untuk menjadi team bola mereka.

programme.title: Jalan-Jalan Makan Angin (2019) Ep05
programme.desc: Pengacara Akhmal Nazri dan Atu Zero menjelajah ke Selangor sambil mempromosi beberapa tempat penginapan dilengkapi kemudahan dan aktiviti menarik bagi percutian dan pelancongan. Antaranya ialah: 1. Sarang By The Brook, K. Kubu Bharu : -Konsep kontena dikelilingi hutan alam semulajadi, kemudahan asas termasuk penghawa dingin dan tempat tidur. -Bilik serendah RM180/ malam. -Aktiviti : Jungle tracking, mandi sungai. 2. Dusun Bonda, Batang Kali : -Konsep berkhemah dikelilingi kolam dan alam semulajadi, suasana kampung, penghawa dingin, private garden, tandas peribadi -Bilik studio : tandas persendirian, dapur, sungai, -Aktiviti : BBQ, makan malam di atas bumbung dengan suasana romantik, sarapan pagi di tepi sungai, melihat ladang madu kelulut. -Bilik serendah RM350/ malam.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep15
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam (Angah) dan Mizan (Along) dua beradik dari satu keluarga. Nizam lulusan luar negeri, bekerjaya, baru berkahwin dan baru juga bercerai. Hubungan Nizam dan Mizan tidak mesra sangat. ibu bapa mereka juga memelihara Hani, sebagai adik angkat. Kini, Hani seorang gadis, selain sangat disayangi ibu bapa mereka, Mizan pula mencintainya. Jalinan percintaan mereka juga direstui ibu bapa mereka, cuma Nizam terpaksa menangguhkan perkahwinan mereka sekurang-kurangnya 3 tahun kerana melanjutkan pelajaran keluar negara. Hani yang baik sahsiahnya dan berbudi pekerti, pandai mengemas rumah tangga memahaminya dan sanggup menunggu. Di hari ketibaan Nizam pulang, ibu bapanya telah menetapkan sebagai hari perkahwinan Nizam dan Hani. Selain majlis telah siap, tetamu juga telah dijemput, tiba-tiba sehari sebelum majlis berlangsung, Nizam meminta majlis dibatalkan dengan alasan dia telah berkahwin 5 bulan lalu. Di hari itu, Mizan juga pulang sebagai meraikan majlis adiknya, lalu ibu bapanya mencadangkan Mizan menggantikan tempat Nizam. Mizan agak terkejut dan tidak bersetuju walau pun dirayu demi menutup maruah keluarga. Sementara itu Hani amat berduka, tetapi sebelah malamnya Hani berubah hati semata-mata demi maruah keluarga lalu merayu beberapa kali kepada Mizan mengambilnya sebagai isteri. Mizan bukan sahaja menolak permintaan Hani, sebaliknya mencerca Hani yang dianggap tidak malu. Hani pula terus berdoa. Di awal pagi hari majlis, Mizan berubah hati dan bersetuju. Majlis perkahwinan Mizan dan Hani serta jamuan berjalan lancar. Di sebelah petangnya. Nizam dan isterinya, Shela juga tiba dan mereka dijangka akan tinggal di situ beberapa ketika.

programme.desc: Ezgi dan zgr, yang melihat polis di hadapan mereka, terkejut. zgr, yang menganggap Tolga mengadu tentang Ezgi, menjadi gila. Mereka semua perlu pergi ke balai polis bersama-sama. Walaupun Ezgi, yang keterangannya diambil, dikeluarkan, mereka tidak melepaskan kerja ini dan cuba membuktikan Ezgi tidak bersalah. Terhadap semua kesukaran, perkara yang paling penting bagi zgr dan Ezgi ialah cinta mereka antara satu sama lain. Tetapi Tolga dan Serdar tidak berniat untuk membiarkan mereka bersendirian. Sementara itu, Ezgi telah menyediakan pesta bujang mengejut untuk Cansu. Cansu sangat gembira dapat berseronok dengan gadis-gadis itu. Emre juga tidak berdiam diri dan menyediakan kejutan untuk Levent. Tetapi kejutan ini tidak akan menggembirakan gadis-gadis itu.

programme.title: Adiwiraku
programme.desc: Adiwiraku berdasarkan kisah benar guru Cheryl Ann Fernando dan perjuangan serta kejayaannya mengajar di sebuah sekolah luar bandar di Kedah. programme.desc: Cansu dan Deniz terkejut apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa Ezgi pergi ke Gcek dengan zgr mengikut perjanjian. Walaupun Ozan menyedari dia telah menumpahkan rahsia itu pada saat-saat akhir, dia perlu menjelaskan segala-galanya dengan tekanan Deniz. Cansu dan Deniz tidak selesa. Oleh kerana mereka takut bahawa Ezgi akan jatuh cinta dengan zgr, mereka mengejar mereka dan pergi ke Gcek. Sementara itu, hari yang penuh dengan pengembaraan dan ketegangan menanti Ezgi dan zgr, yang jatuh di pulau terbiar akibat masalah yang mereka alami, dan rakan serta keluarga mereka yang tidak dapat menghubungi mereka sedang mencari mereka di merata tempat dengan panik.

programme.title: Nargil Ep06
programme.desc: The grandfather makes a concoction to get the dark magic out of the heart of Nargil, Lengeh and Leeveh. Haleh also plans to take something from her grandfather's lab. She does not even have a tiny clue that how dangerous this will be.

programme.title: Gila Baby
programme.desc: Bob memerlukan wang yang banyak bagi membiayai kos pembedahan ayahnya di hospital. Dengan mengambil jalan mudah, Bob membantu Roy, bekas teman sekelasnya di sekolah yang selalu membulinya dahulu untuk melakukan jenayah mencuri kereta. Walaupun percubaan pertama Bob untuk aktiviti jenayah tersebut berjaya tetapi ada seorang bayi di tempat duduk belakang kereta yang dicurinya itu! Bob kini mendapati dirinya diburu oleh beberapa pihak yang tidak akan berhenti selagi Bob dan bayi tersebut tidak ditangkap! Untuk mengeruhkan lagi keadaan, dalam perjalanan menyelamatkan diri, Bob bertemu Jaja yang mengugut Bob untuk membawanya sekali kerana ingin lari dari masalahnya sendiri

Dia perlu menghabiskan wang tersebut dalam masa 21 hari - sekiranya gagal, harta warisan tersebut akan diberi kepada sebuah syarikat. Syaratnya Os tidak boleh membeli aset atau tanah untuk simpanan sendiri. Meski sudah berbelanja boros baki wang masih tersisa.

programme.title: Kembar Siam
programme.desc: Berwajah serupa namun merupakan dua orang yang berbeza. Dua jejaka dengan kehidupan yang berlainan - seorang ingin menjadi pelakon filem terkenal namun gagal manakala seorang lagi merupakan pelakon filem terkenal namun mengimpikan kebebasan. Mereka bertemu dan merancang sesuatu yang malangnya hanya telah menimbulkan kekacauan dan kekeliruan orang sekeliling.

programme.title: Juara
programme.desc: Empat beradik membawa haluan masing-masing selepas bapa mereka dimasukkan ke sebuah hospital sakit jiwa. Malik memilih untuk menjadi peninju manakala Sidi memilih jalan gelap dan diperalatkan sindiket pencurian berlian. Malik memenangi pertandingan tinju anjuran Joe Martino. Adiknya, Sidi dipaksa untuk bertarung dengan Malik jika tidak mahu kehilangan keluarganya.

programme.title: Sengketa Cinta
programme.desc: Malik menembak dua orang pembelot setelah diarah oleh Chief. Malik dan Amir, anak Datuk Ali di mana keduanya rakan lama bertemu semula di sebuah kelab malam. Persengketaan berlaku antara Chief dan Malik apabila dia dilihat sebagai pembelot yang telah mencuri wang kumpulan Chief.

programme.title: Cikgu Romantik
programme.desc: Bercita-cita ingin menjadi selebriti terkenal, Azizah mendapat surat uji bakat yang bertempat di Kuala Lumpur. Dia pun pergi dan menetap di rumah temannya, Tila lalu berkenalan bersama seorang guru vokal iaitu Ramli. Muncul pula Shahrul yang mengatakan bahawa raut wajah Azizah seiras dengan isterinya yang telah meninggal dunia.

programme.title: Orang Kampung Otak Kimia
programme.desc: Dipandang rendah oleh keluarga dan masyarakat kerana gagal dalam peperiksaan, Os mula mencipta satu formula. Os yang bijak dalam kimia dan biologi, mencipta formula yang membolehkan haiwan dan orang bisu boleh berkata-kata. Penemuan tersebut mula menarik minat seorang ahli perniagaan - namun malangnya dia ditipu.

programme.title: Janda Meletup
programme.desc: Rosnah, seorang janda muda cuba dipikat oleh Kamil yang tertarik dengannya namun gagal. Samad yang berasal dari Kuala Lumpur pergi ke kampung untuk mencari pembantu rumah dan bertemu Rosnah yang ingin bekerja dengannya. Kamil yang kecewa pergi ke Kuala Lumpur untuk berjumpa Rosnah selain tekadnya yang ingin bekerja dan mengahwini Rosnah. Suatu insiden terjadi menyebabkan Rosnah dan Kamil berganding bahu untuk menyelamatkan Samad.

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Kisah seorang graduan universiti bekerja sebagai budak pejabat yang pada suatu hari didatangi oleh seekor monyet cerdik tersesat ke rumahnya. Suatu hari berlaku krisis di pejabatnya. Budak pejabat itu perlu segera mencari jalan untuk menyelesaikan masalah dan dalam proses itu hampir membahayakan nyawanya sendiri. Dengan bantuan monyet tersebut, dia berjaya mengatasi banyak masalah dan berjaya menyelamatkan pekerjaannya.

programme.title: Keluarga 99

Percutian mereka di Kuala Lumpur bertukar menjadi sebuah pengembaraan apabila terlibat sebagai saksi kes penculikan. Sekumpulan mafia menculik anak hartawan bernama Rahim. They both wished each other would disappear from their lives; however, they are neighbors. Pei-Pei and Yu-Hsuan have been fighting, yet they inevitably fell into the destined love with each other. If fighting against each other is a way of communication and caring, then these quarrelsome lovers are getting closer and growing together. When they gradually start to let go of their competitive attitude that is full of hostility, they even start to click with each other!

programme.title: Stylish Man-The Chef (M) Ep3399
programme.desc: <Stylish Man The Chef> is co-hosted by the Golden Bell Awards winner Sam Tseng, Bernice Tsai and Genie Chuo, together with two professional chefs, A-Chi and James. There are two main themes for the program, which are Big Stars Come to Cook and Five-Star Cooking Show. <Stylish Man The Chef> containing not only the bomb of laughter, but the audience can also gain practical cooking knowledge throughout the program.

programme.title: The Tradition Story of Taiwan (T) Ep47524753
programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation

programme.title: In the Family (T) Ep249250
programme.desc: "Home" as axis X and "love" as axis Y, this piece exquisitely depicts the ups and downs in life of an ordinary family. From touching sibling love, to the struggles and entanglement of parent-child relationship, the show elaborates on the importance of encountering the surroundings with a positive attitude. Through a bowl of beef noodle soup, Hui-wen and Chien-chin teach their four daughters, Spring, Summer, Fall, and Winter, how to behave around others. The heartwarming play is relaxing, fun, humorous, and a tearjerker.

programme.title: Hot Door Night (M) Ep1866
programme.desc: Different in age, generation, and hosting style, these three hosts not only can sing, act, dance, and imitate, but are also skilled in cross-talk! With this unique combination, we hope to attract viewers of all ages and spark great entertainment.

programme.title: iWalker (M) Ep17
programme.desc: iWalker is a TV program which introduce food and attractive places to audience.

programme.title: Home Sweet Home
programme.desc: A school bus accident kills almost everyone on board. The bus driver got injured and partially lost his memory while rescuing one of the boys. To thank the driver, the boys dad, Wang, brings him to live with the family in their basement. However, the driver soon discovers strange behaviours from the Wangs which seem to be related to the accident.

programme.title: Flirting Scholar 2
programme.desc: The movie tells the story of Tang Bo Hu and his three buddies before they become the four great talents in Jiangnan. Tang Bo Hu encounters a beautiful girl when studying in a monastery and they quickly fall in love, but her hidden identity is accidentally unveiled when Tang and friends uncover a conspiracy at the monastery.

programme.title: VR Fighter
programme.desc: Bodyguard Long Wei has posttraumatic stress disorder after his wife's death. One day, he encounters Amy who works for a VR technology firm and is invited for a new product test. After the test, Long Wei becomes the firms VR fighter and dons the newly invented armour. However, as mysterious armed men break in, a fierce battle has just begun...

programme.title: 12 Golden Ducks
programme.desc: This is a comeback story about the misadventures of a group of gigolos, led by Future, trying to make their mark in Hong Kong. As with any profession, they have their share of setbacks, but their ability to find laughter within the tears reflects the drive, passion and the indomitable spirit of the Hong Kong people.

programme.title: A Witness out of the Blue
programme.desc: The police suspects that a jewel thief, found dead in his unit with all stolen goods missing, is killed by his gang leader. They also found the crime to be related to a jewel robbery many months ago, with the robbers involved being killed off one by one. In this complicated case, the polices only witness is a talking parrot from the crime scene.

programme.title: Blind War
programme.desc: Former SWAT captain Dong Gu suffers traumatic visual loss during a failed mission for which he is forced to take responsibility. He manages to get over and adapt to the situation with his daughters company, until his nemesis appears and puts his daughter in danger. Despite being blind, Dong Gu must fight to save his daughter.

programme.title: Social Distancing
programme.desc: Cherry is a young girl addicted to the internet. After seeing a warning video about an e-ghost on YouTube, she begins to encounter many mysterious incidents, and the e-ghost also takes control of her family. Cherry must face her unbearable past in order to get out of this horrifying paranormal world...

programme.title: Song of the Assassins
programme.desc: A young assassin is assigned his first mission while secretly investigating the cause of his familys massacre years ago. While taking on the mission, he finds himself entangled in a political conspiracy that was planned for years and has to use his skills as an assassin to solve whatever comes his way.

programme.title: The Rookies
programme.desc: An extreme sports lover accidentally gets involved in an illegal trading activity by international crime syndicates. Led by international special agent Bruce, he forms an amateur unit with a police officer, an inventor and a doctor to fight the crime syndicates together, leading to a series of thrilling and hilarious adventures.

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: Mosaic, an urban sketcher, is suffering from ALS and wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. When Mosaic reunites with his old classmate Angelfish, whom he has a crush on since primary school, he asks her to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day. Will Angelfish say yes?

programme.title: Touch of the Light
programme.desc: A blind but talented pianist Siang encounters an unrecognized but skilful dancer Chieh. Chieh is attracted to the courageous Siang while Siang is fascinated by the adventurous Chieh. Their friendship grows as Siang and Chieh pursue their dreams together. Sandrine Pinna was awarded Best Actress for her role as Chieh in the 2012 Taipei Film Festival.

programme.title: Princess & 7 Kung Fu Masters
programme.desc: Seven Kung Fu masters live in Lucky Town, the only safe residing place in northeast China. When warlord Lam refuses to side with the Japanese, an agent is assigned to take over his army and kill his daughter using ninjutsu. Lams daughter escapes and seeks help from the seven masters, who finally defeat the enemy and save the warlord!

programme.title: Shock Wave 2
programme.desc: A series of bomb explosions is causing fear in Hong Kong. Former bomb specialist Feng is found in coma at the crime scene and becomes a suspect. To prove his innocence, he seeks help from his former partner Wen. However, it seems revealing the truth is as risky as disposing a bomb

programme.title: Wolf Pack
programme.desc: The Wolf Pack squad led by Lao Diao, is a foreign-based team that specializes in overseas security jobs. In one of the missions, the squad discovers that a terrorist force is planning to destroy the countrys energy source. Lao Diao is now entrusted with the task of leading his squad to fight back. Can the Wolf Pack save the day?

programme.title: Ready O/R Knot
programme.desc: Guy and Heidi have been together for five years since they first met in a wedding banquet, but marriage soon becomes a challenge to their relationship. Heidi sees marriage as a testimony of their love, while Guy sees it as doomsday. Can the couple resolve their conflict? Are they ready or not?

programme.title: Ride On
programme.desc: Master Luo, a washed-up stuntman, trains his beloved horse Red Hare to be a stunt horse. Due to his debts though, Red Hare may be taken away by the debtors. Master Luo has no choice but to seek help from his estranged daughter, and the incident ends up becoming a golden opportunity for them to reconcile.

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: A 28-year-old IT geek has only been in love once. Surprisingly, he ends up getting romantically involved with five different women this year and the one thing they have in common is that they all live in far flung areas of Hong Kong. After taking five intensive relationship courses within these 365 days, will he find the-one?

programme.title: My Country, My Parents
programme.desc: Set in 4 different eras in China, the 4-part anthology about home and country is directed by Wu Jing, Zhang Zi Yi, Xu Zheng and Shen Teng, who also star in their own story. The movie depicts how the fathers forge ahead through the struggle of times, defending strong family ties and passing on the fighting spirit through generations.

programme.title: Red Line
programme.desc: A former professional car racer, Le falls into despair after causing his brother's death in a car race, until he meets female doctor Hui and becomes an ambulance driver who vows to save lives with speed. Meanwhile, the truth about his brothers accident emerges with the investigation of Le's three good friends...

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. While things seem to be falling apart, this dinner may well be an opportunity to mend relations.

programme.title: Hand Rolled Cigarette
programme.desc: A retired British-Chinese soldier becomes a target in a triad manhunt when he takes in a young South Asian man who carries a bag of stolen drugs. Forced to live together, the two men transcend conflicts and cultural differences to form a beautiful friendship in this poignant tale of loyalty and brotherhood.

programme.title: Another Me
programme.desc: Constable Li Mao marries a rich girl but her parents disapprove of their marriage. One day, Li accidentally discovers that he looks exactly like the prince! While he aims to secure a high ranking position in the palace, the prince wants freedom, so they decide to switch identities. This however, got them both involved in the ministers conspiracy

programme.title: Keep Rolling
programme.desc: Directorial debut of Man Lim Chung, who spent 3 years filming this documentary about the life and filmmaking philosophy of Ann Hui, one of Hong Kongs greatest filmmakers. It traces Huis life story and her 40-year careers ups and downs using film footages, candid conversations with Hui, and interviews with her collaborators, family and friends.

programme.title: Reunion Dinner
programme.desc: Chao Yang and Zi Hong are soon to wed but both have not met the others parents. When a client requests for a livestream of their reunion dinner to promote his products, it set the stage for their parents first meeting. Estranged from his mother, Yang decides to rent a family for the dinner which results in a series of mishaps and hilarity.

programme.title: The Narrow Road
programme.desc: Chak, a small cleaning company owner, hits tough times during the pandemic. In need of an assistant, he hires a young single mother Candy, who unexpectedly helps him solve many difficulties at work. While life seems to get back on track, a series of cruel realities happen again, but they still bond together to support each other on the narrow road.

programme.title: Cliff Walkers
programme.desc: The first spy thriller movie by famous Director Zhang Yi Mou, this film follows four Communist Party special agents who embark on a secret operation in the Japanese puppet state of Manchukuo in 1932. Sold out by a traitor, the agents, who split up into two teams, find themselves surrounded by threats on all sides. Can they complete their mission?

programme.title: Red Line
programme.desc: A former professional car racer, Le falls into despair after causing his brother's death in a car race, until he meets female doctor Hui and becomes an ambulance driver who vows to save lives with speed. Meanwhile, the truth about his brothers accident emerges with the investigation of Le's three good friends...

programme.title: 77 Heartwarmings
programme.desc: After breaking up with Adam, Eva focuses on her career but Adam still wants to make up and tries to move her 77 times. Things become more complicated when a Thai movie idol courts Eva. It is at this time that Evas mother becomes very ill, and she considers marriage in order to fulfil her mothers wish. Will Adam succeed in warming Evas heart?

programme.title: The White Storm 2: Drug Lords
programme.desc: In this epic action-thriller starring Andy Lau and Louis Koo, the two award-winning best actors star on opposing sides of a drug war. As a bounty of $100 million Hong Kong dollars is made to hunt down the biggest drug dealer in the city, Hong Kong becomes the battleground for the fight between good and evil.

programme.title: Queen of Triads
programme.desc: An innocent young girl named Zuo Lan attempts to commit suicide after she was betrayed by her boyfriend. However, she is saved by a gangster boss called Zui Ge. In order to exact her revenge, Zuo Lan joins force with Zui Ge and becomes a top mobster

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon (2020)
programme.desc: In 1960s Hong Kong, rookie cop Xu Le cracks a robbery but gets demoted instead, as this offends a corrupt inspector. Xu meets a rich girl Bai who falls instantly in love with him one day. Will he break up with his childhood girlfriend for Bai so as to climb the social ladder, and how does Xu eventually become one of Hong Kongs legendary detective?

programme.title: The Wandering Earth II
programme.desc: In this prequel, humans build enormous engines on the Earths surface to find a new home when the sun is burning out. In the dangerous universe, a group of young people has to step forward once again to fight in the critical battle to save the Earth.

programme.title: All Men are Brothers
programme.desc: This is a sequel to Chang Chehs epic The Water Margin, and follows the patriotic story of seven warriors in the band of 108 outlaws at Mount Liang. The magnificent seven battle against the despotic government officials to save their country.

programme.title: The Human Goddess
programme.desc: This is a love story between an alluring fairy, Seventh Sister, who comes down from heaven to experience life in 70s Hong Kong, and a man who is running a debt laden orphanage. A heartless tycoon plans to take over the orphanage for its land but has to deal with Seventh Sisters magical powers as she aims to protect it from falling into his hands!

programme.title: The Sword Stained with Royal Blood
programme.desc: Adapted from Jin Yongs novel, the movie depicts the havoc breaking out in the martial arts world when a warrior on the run uncovers a sword, a training manual, a treasure map and a secret message on the body of a deceased martial arts master.

programme.title: Guess Who Killed My Twelve Lovers?
programme.desc: Jenny Hu, Shaw Brothers' gorgeous Chinese-German star, was given her first comedy role in the wild and wacky Guess Who Killed My Twelve Lovers? Described as "a comedy of belly laughs and chilling murders", it is a unique entry in the Hong Kong theater of the absurd.

programme.title: The Boxer From The Temple
programme.desc: A young monk, The Kid, was expelled from the temple due to his crazy ways. After leaving the temple, he fights a cruel bandit's son and befriends a prostitute. As he fights for justice, his Crazy Lo Han Fist improves with every fight.

programme.title: Twinkle Twinkle Little Star
programme.desc: A beautiful but ignorant woman is abducted by aliens but nobody believes her close encounter. While planning a suicide to prove herself, she meets a failed detective who is also planning his suicide. They change their minds about dying after finding each other and start to encounter bizarre adventures, before falling in love with each other.

programme.title: Shaolin Mantis
programme.desc: The Emperor orders Feng to find proofs of Master Tians rebellion in his house. Feng falls in love with Tians granddaughter and marries her. When he finds the proofs and tries to leave with her, his wife is killed in the fight against Tian. Feng creates the mantis-style martial arts and vows to avenge her death.

programme.title: My Son
programme.desc: Kuo, a polices son, blames his father for his mothers death. He has no job, spends time in night clubs and always gets into fights. One night, Kuo rescues Mei from being raped and they become friends. Kuo wants to support Mei and her family so he goes gambling hoping to gain more money but bad luck seems to be following them with tragic outcomes.

programme.title: The Convict Killer
programme.desc: After spending fifteen years in prison on trumped-up charges for drug smuggling, the martial arts master Teng Piao embarks on a journey to take revenge on the person who sets him up - Black Leopard. Unfortunately for Piao, no one knows the real identity of Black Leopard, except that there is a black leopard tattoo on his chest.

programme.title: King Drummer
programme.desc: A young musician Chi Chiang is hired by the manager of a popular band when the group's drummer/leader Charlie, quits to join a rival group. The new drummer becomes an immediate hit, causing Charlie to be very jealous. Furthermore, the young drummer's mother is dead set against him having a music career.

programme.title: Inside The Forbidden City
programme.desc: Justice Bao discovers that Consort Lis new born son was swapped at birth and that she was expelled from the palace by Empress Liu twenty years ago. He sets Eunuch Guo up to confess his conspiracy with the Empress. Empress Liu is convicted for her act and Consort Li finally reunites with her son who is now the Emperor.

programme.title: The Fake Ghost Catchers
programme.desc: This delightful action comedy featuring international favourite Alexander Fu Sheng premiered two years before the American hit Ghostbusters was released. Is it a coincidence? You be the judge as you enjoy this amazing showcase of wushu and wizardry.

programme.title: Enchanting Shadow
programme.desc: A young scholar Ning spends the night in a creepy temple that is said to be haunted. He does not believe in the rumours, but soon meets a beautiful female ghost Nie. Nie is forced to stay in the temple to seduce young men for a powerful demon to feast on. Knowing Nie to be a kind ghost, Ning decides to help her escape from the demons clutches.

programme.title: The Iron Buddha
programme.desc: After a notorious rapist Xiao kills his master and the entire clan, Han the last surviving disciple, decides to take revenge. He must find the legendary Hulong Blade to counter Xiao's Evil Poisonous Sword, but as Han has never seen Xiao before, he is deceived when Xiao poses as an ally to try and steal his Blade in the process.

programme.title: Sex, Love and Hate
programme.desc: This masterpiece spins three interconnected tales about Hong Kong society's differing views on love and what women want from love. Follow a trio of Hong Kong women as they explore relationships and fulfil their hopes of finding true love.

programme.title: Shaolin Hand Lock
programme.desc: Li Cheng Yings father was set up and killed by his old friend Ling Hao. Li, who has learnt Shaolin Hand Lock from his father, is on a mission to avenge his death. He works as an undercover guard at Lings house where he meets his long-lost brother, and the two team up to take revenge for their father against Ling.

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: This is an epic tale set during the time of the Sino-Japanese war. A painter Yu saves a young girl, Lotus, who is being sold to a brothel. They fall in love, get married and settled in to a peaceful life. However, their life is soon shattered by the Japanese invasion and the brutal regime that follows.

programme.title: The Proud Twins
programme.desc: Jiang Xiao Yu is separated from his twin brother as a baby after his parents are murdered. He is taken by a couple to Villains Valley and raised to be a villain by a host of outlaws. Jiang leaves the valley to explore the world when he grows up - will he be able to avenge his parents and meet with his twin brother?

programme.title: Rear Entrance
programme.desc: Mrs Xu is childless and watches a lonely little girl playing at the rear entrance from afar every day. She warmly nurtures the girl and even adopts her from her uncaring parent. The girl brings happiness to the Xus until her long lost mother appears one day and to make her happy, Mrs Xu reluctantly lets the girl reunite with her mother.

programme.title: King Eagle
programme.desc: A young swordman, King Eagle, unwillingly gets involved in the internal affairs of a powerful clan and becomes their target. He is saved by the female chief of the clan, Lin, and falls in love with her. However, Lins sister is part of all evil plots and betrays her. Even so, Lin begs King Eagle not to harm her sister.

programme.title: The Story of Sue San
programme.desc: TIn this Huangmei Opera romance, Wang is the son of a respected government official whereas Sue San is a famous prostitute. Although they love each other and seem to be perfectly matched, the two are worlds apart when it comes to social ranking, which will prove hard to overcome...

programme.title: Disciples Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Yi is a skilled disciple of the Hong Quan style kung fu who work in a textile mill recommended by his senior, Han. Han warns Yi not to show off his martial arts skill so as to avoid getting into trouble. However, Yi does not listen and eventually gets dangerously involved in the conflict between two opposing textile mills.

programme.title: Summer Heat
programme.desc: Aptly described by its original title of "Money, Sex And Love", this is a gripping drama about Judy, a woman with a rich husband as well as two lovers who happen to be brothers. Jenny Hu is Judy, and her knockout beauty makes this summer sizzle...

programme.title: Life Gamble
programme.desc: Martial arts master Yu has retired for years but is invited to join force with another master Tao to fight against the four famous thieves and retrieve the stolen Dragon Jade. However, Taos real plan is to possess the treasure himself and kills Yu after he defeats the thieves...

programme.title: The Venus' Tear Diamond
programme.desc: Legendary rival jewel thieves Fragrant Night and Nocturnal Earl travel to Japan to steal the famous Venus Tear Diamond. They fall quickly in love at first sight, without knowing the other person is their rival and is after the same prize. Who will get the diamond, and will it mean the end of their new found love?

programme.title: Super Inframan
programme.desc: Transformed from a young laboratory researcher, the thunderbolt-fisted Inframan must battle Princess Dragon Mom who wakes up from hibernation to conquer the earth with her army of mutant monsters.

programme.title: Forever Diamonds
programme.desc: Hua, a pretty fraud, steals a brilliant diamond ring from a shop in Hong Kong and escapes to Singapore. To smuggle the ring pass customs, Hua slips it into the pocket of a stranger, Yen, but then lost track of him. Hua finally spots Yen after searching for days and does everything to get close to him in order to take the ring back.

programme.title: The Kung-fu Instructor
programme.desc: Wong Yang is a famous martial artist who is forced to teach kung fu to the Mong Clan, an evil clan which is trying to destroy its nemesis, the Chow Clan. Chow Ping from the Chow Clan is a student of Wongs caught in the Mongs territory and as punishment, the Mong Clan wants to cut off Chow Pings limbs. Wong steps in to defend his student.

programme.title: The Perfumed Arrow
programme.desc: A charming Huangmei Opera title, this is the story of Fei E, a Generals daughter who grows up fooling everyone that she is a boy, including her two closest schoolmates. When she has to choose one of them to marry, how will Fei E tell them that she is a girl? To complicate matters, a girl who Fei E saves one day only wants to be married to her!

programme.title: The Bloody Escape
programme.desc: Ku is a skilled Kung Fu artist brought up by the bandits and does not agree with the brutal leader of the bandits camp. He rescues Tong, a young lady forced to become the leaders wife, causing both the authorities and bandits to come after them. Ku has to stand up against the bandits that he grew up with so as to start a new life for himself.

programme.title: River of Tears
programme.desc: Retired singer Fang lives happily with her husband and son. Tragedy happens when a man from her past returns to haunt her. In an ensuing struggle to free her from his clutches, her husband dies in a car accident. Blamed by her father-in-law for her husbands death, Fang gets chased out of the house and goes back to singing to make a living...

programme.title: The Villains
programme.desc: Hung is an orphan seeking help from her wealthy uncle who has two sons but only dotes on the younger son Feng, a playboy. Feng covets the beauty of Hung and rapes her but when she gets pregnant, Hung is wrongfully accused and gets sent off by her uncle to protect Feng. Will Feng be punished for his villainy?

programme.title: The Dream of the Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the most widely read and filmed novel in Chinese history, this sumptuous version was said to be the most successful one. Loh Tihs looks, demeanour and aura in her portrayal of Lin Dai Yu has won her the epithet "Classic Beauty".

programme.title: The Lady Hermit
programme.desc: The Lady Hermit hides away for years to plot revenge after being defeated by the evil Black Knight. Young swordswoman Tsui Ping is determined to take down Black Knight herself and begs Lady Hermit to teach her martial arts skills. The Black Knight's days are numbered when the Lady Hermit and her protege perfect the technique to take him down.

programme.title: Crocodile River
programme.desc: This story has a Romeo and Juliet flavour. Two families who hate each other live across the opposite sides of a river filled with crocodiles and do not bother to have a bridge built. Their respective children meet in university and fall in love, but have to find ways to be together and resolve the hatred between their families.

programme.desc: Three Kings Islands/ Manawatwhi - Delve into the strange magic of the Three Kings Islands, a remote archipelago north of New Zealand. programme.title: Beasts of the Big Blue 1 Ep6
programme.desc: Cook Islands/ Kki 'Airani - Travel to the Cook Islands, the destination of choice for 3,000 humpback whales ready to mate and raise their young. Witness giant clams and green turtles thriving in the islands massive coral reef and get a glimpse into our evolutionary past.

programme.title: Wild Dogs: Running with the Pack 1 Ep2

programme.title: Untamed Valley 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Hippo Lagoon - Secluded and sheltered, away from the hustle and bustle of Zambias Luangwa River, Kasikizi lagoon is home to a small community of diverse wildlife. At the height of the wet season, its full to the brim with water a peaceful spot, ideal for two old male hippos who wallow in its watery depths. The lagoon is their sanctuary, a world away from the more violent life theyve left behind at the main river, where they had to face aggressive beachmasters, willing to fight to protect their territory...

programme.title: Untamed Valley 1 Ep2
programme.desc: The Big Bend - The Big Bend is over two miles long one of the biggest meanders along the Luangwa River in Zambia. Its a busy spot - home to a pod of hippos who luxuriate in its deep pools, an important crossing point for elephants and place to drink for huge herds of buffalo.

programme.desc: Bound By Blood - The southwest corner of New Zealands South Island is hemmed in by giant mountains and the rough Pacific Ocean. programme.desc: Pushed to the Limits - Thirst for rain alongside the animals of the Kalahari, as they endure a brutally dry year. Witness co-operation between elephant herds in their desperate search for water and meet a meerkats strange babysitter, who helps the next generation survive.

programme.desc: The Waterways - Some of mightiest rivers in North America originate on the glacial heights of the Rocky Mountains. The lakes, rivers and marshes of the Rockies are like arteries pulsing through the landscape, feeding the creatures that call the mountains home. Fed by glaciers and motivated by gravity, these waterways are split by the massive Rockies, which divert flow into the Atlantic, Pacific, and Arctic Oceans. From the uninhabitable icy pecks, water melts off glaciers, runs down thunderous waterfalls, filters through wetlands, sculpts the terrain, and finally flows out to the ocean, sustaining life and transforming environments along the way.

programme.desc: Why Do Spiders Build Webs? - The friends are having a tidying up day. Spiders are rather nice, rather clean and rather clever.

programme.title: Guess With Jess Ep10
programme.desc: How Can We Bring The Outside Inside? - Poor Willow has a sore hoof and has to stay inside until it's better. She's really missing her orchard so Jess and Mimi are determined to bring something of the outside to Willow to cheer her up. A tree is too big and it's too late in the year for apples. Jess works out that they can make beautiful tree and leaf rubbings into a wonderful tree collage for the stable to remind Willow of her orchard.

programme.title: Guess With Jess Ep11

programme.title: Guess With Jess Ep12

Her treatments for Edwin and Perry turn out to be a bit messier than she expected.

programme.title: Olivia Ep32

programme.title: Olivia Ep33

programme.title: Olivia Ep34

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep9
programme.desc: Why Monkeys Swing In The Trees - You see there was a time when Monkey used to play on the ground and he loved to wind up Crocodile. One day the Big Rains came and Monkey got stranded up the Mango Tree. Nasty Crocodile promised to take him to dry land. But only in exchange for one thing. His HEART! Monkey tricked Crocodile and when Crocodile found out that Monkey swapped his heart for a measley mango, he chased Monkey up a tree. From that day on Monkey swings in the trees keeping well clear of Crocodiles angry snaps! Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep10

Tickbird outwits Hippo by using the tides and from that day she is allowed to sit on Hippo's back and pick off all the yummy ticks she can eat! Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep11
programme.desc: Why Frog Croaks - You see there was a time when Frog didn't croak. Frog sang like a bird and the birds didn't like it. Birds were the masters of song and that's the way it should be! So the birds trick poor old Frog into a singing duel and sing and sing and sing until poor old Frog's voice is reduced to a rebbit. Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep12
programme.desc: Why Spider Has A Tiny Waist - You see there was a time when Spider didn't have a tiny waist. She was all big and round and did she like her food! One day greedy Spider hears of Four Feasts in Tinga Tinga and she wanted to go to them all! So she spun four threads and attached them to various animals going to the feasts. But the Monkeys, Frog, Hippo and the Bees all set off in different directions North, South, East and West and Spider's thread soon runs out. EEeeek! The threads get tighter and tighter and tighter, making Spider's smaller and smaller and smaller! Luckily the threads break, but from that day on Spider has always had a tiny waist. Tales from Africa.
